metadata.name: Essences
metadata.description:
The Essences picture is a reflection of the two entities we are moving
Here you're watching them touch each other closely.
It's a very special experience for me and for each person.
I have shown my state and feeling that my angel is firmly holding and controlling my demon.
Sometimes that fine line can be torn off....
Looking at this picture you will know yourself better and remind yourself who and how manages your state and eradicate your bad emotions and impulses that in one second can destroy you
